Package resource

This package defines the different types of resources that will be used in the program

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Resource
    Interface for all the resources that will be used at the pool
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Basket
    This class defines a basket that will be used by the swimmers to put their clothes inside
    BasketPool
    This class defines a pool where the baskets of the swimming pool are stored
    Cubicle
    This class defines a cubicle where the swimmers will change their clothes
    CubiclePool
    This class defines a pool where the cubicles of the swimming pool are stored
    FreeResourceAction<R extends Resource>  
    ResourcefulUser<R extends Resource>
    this class creates the user of the differents resources
    ResourcePool<R extends Resource>
    This class defines a Resource pool which manages all the resources of the pool wheter there are availables or not
    TakeResourceAction<R extends Resource>
    This class defines a TakeResourceAction that will take baskets and cubicles from the different pools, and it gives them to an user
